race.description: Bet365 Bet Boost Hwt Maiden Plate
race.comment: TRUE TEST (5) wound up strongly last time out to finish a nose adrift over 2100m at Horsham. Enjoyed the step up in journey and he can go one better for the Paul Preusker yard. HONEYJOY (7) let down in good style last start beaten 1.7L  at Warrnambool over 2000m. This is a suitable assignment and she's a threat. BERNIE BEEL (2) was vet-cleared after an inglorious run at Warrnambool, but ran and improved effort there the one prior. That would have him in the finish here. ALCAPARCI (1) had been off the scene for a long time and can go better second up. He needs to find plenty to be winning, all the same.
